{"tid":365042,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"唔反黑警3日，多謝黑警","createTime":"2017-08-19T02:24:31.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-19T03:22:15.000Z","uid":54373,"like":4,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"be90efa248f2744e825624155205b66bba52bcfd","tid":365042,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-19T02:24:31.000Z","msg":"你既坐監<br />\n令廣大煙民唔洗犯法訂煙<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n生產和銷售IQOS的煙草商Philip Morris 發言人，他指出目前加熱煙IQOS在全球25個國家和地區上市，但暫未引入香港，澄清在港市面出售的IQOS並非其公司正式入口，對於海關接連掃蕩，認為反映這款煙在港有需求，公司亦正與海關搓商，希望盡快將該款煙引入本港。"},{"pid":"7d2afc9ead5275f44e1717e319ac02225f77bdd8","tid":365042,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-19T02:29:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"faf4a7fc57898dc5e3cc253c0323df93da3d5219","tid":365042,"uid":119349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-19T02:29:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/41.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"41862772e3b2b94c8796aebfed45a491d9333305","tid":365042,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-19T02:33:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"31d6752e25d0d38d241a272836b6079e5ae1263b","tid":365042,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-19T03:14:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b5b4f73ee9fa0197d6c23b24dcd0055111b8b6f1","tid":365042,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-19T03:22:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}